u%E1%BB%B7-V%C3%A2n-%C4%91%E1%BA%A1o-nh%C3%A2n/poem-yHHAatIXQ3-AfHqHiEYdJg">Thứ vận tặng Thuỷ Vân đạo nhân - 次韻贈水雲道人</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Chu-V%C4%83n-An/author-AWz2bPtWqcz6Jh2YwzaErA">Chu Văn An</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%E1%BB%91ng-C%E1%BB%91-b%C3%A1t-ph%C3%A2n-v%C4%83n-h%E1%BB%8Dc-th%C3%ADch-H%E1%BB%93ng-C%C3%A1t-ch%C3%A2u/poem-HrYvDephDpfYnIZl-V2i2g">Tống Cố bát phân văn học thích Hồng Cát châu - 送顧八分文學適洪吉州</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%E1%BB%91ng-D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-l%E1%BB%A5c-ph%C3%A1n-quan-s%E1%BB%A9-t%C3%A2y-phi%C3%AAn/poem-Eln7UzT_jIi6xc1ZwNyliA">Tống Dương lục phán quan sứ tây phiên - 送楊六判官使西蕃</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Khi%C3%AAm/T%E1%BB%91ng-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-th%C6%B0-S%C3%A0i-Trang-Khanh-t%E1%BB%B1/poem-zD7mrwO-43MIHObHTaGOMw">Tống thượng thư Sài Trang Khanh tự - 送尚書柴莊卿序</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Khi%C3%AAm/author-1_5YGABQESnAmYdOvhbEZQ">Lý Khiêm</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-H%C3%A0nh/T%E1%BB%A9-s%E1%BA%A7u-thi/poem-DU-Xoj-ZhfCDiwOq0PYG-A">Tứ sầu thi - 四愁詩</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-H%C3%A0nh/author-L37GQHbELmLdeisdE7nPzQ">Trương Hành</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
